---
title: Roasted Pumpkin & Crumbly Cheese Pizza with Caramelised Onion & Rocket-Pear Salad
description: This pizza combines bright, roasted veggies and two types of cheese for a flavourful vegetarian 'Za'. It might not be pizza as
Italians know it, but it sure does hit the spot.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/roasted-pumpkin-and-feta-pizza-51843ea4.jpg
